00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:10,740
Um...And now?

584
00:38:10,750 --> 00:38:13,850
My wife's got lymphoma.
Uh, stage III.

585
00:38:13,850 --> 00:38:18,990
And, uh, lately,
the state of things, uh...

586
00:38:18,980 --> 00:38:23,040
Well, sometimes, I...
Late at night...

587
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:28,050
I wonder if maybe
the sickness of this world,

588
00:38:28,050 --> 00:38:31,990
if it isn't inside my wife
somehow.

589
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:34,940
The -- the cancer.

590
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:37,320
I don't -- I don't know

