00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:33,980
You, uh, you didn't hear?

605
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:35,640
No.

606
00:40:35,650 --> 00:40:38,390
Well, got worried,
so I let myself in.

607
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:40,380
Mm.

608
00:40:40,380 --> 00:40:41,740
You feeling okay?

609
00:40:41,750 --> 00:40:43,390
Oh, sure.

610
00:40:45,950 --> 00:40:47,890
Little tired.

