A rhinoceros?

644
00:42:18,220 --> 00:42:20,120
Yeah, it's Charlie.

645
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:22,690
I'm looking for dad.

646
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:25,680
Well, is he --
when's he coming back?

647
00:42:28,950 --> 00:42:30,750
No, that's --

648
00:42:33,380 --> 00:42:36,880
J-just tell him that I'm --
I'm ready for school,

649
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,680
to go back.

650
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:41,110
I want to go, like he said.

651
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:48,220
Okay, then.

652
00:44:26,080 --> 00:44:27,810
Ed!

653
00:44:33,550 --> 00:44:35,590
Ed!

654
00:44:39,350 --> 00:44:40,920
Oh, no! No!

655
00:44:53,880 --> 00:44:56,040
Uhh!

656
00:46:00,280 --> 00:46:02,540
Aah!

657
00:46:14,780 --> 00:46:17,610
Noreen. Noreen, you okay?

658
00:46:17,620 --> 00:46:20,820
You okay?
Come on. Come on.

659
00:46:22,650 --> 00:46:24,050
Ed!

660
00:46:27,380 --> 00:46:28,780
Ed!

661
00:46:30,450 --> 00:46:33,190
Ed!

662
00:46:36,280 --> 00:46:39,010
