about the world?

685
00:48:48,050 --> 00:48:52,080
Being grown's got a price.

686
00:48:52,080 --> 00:48:54,550
Kid gets slapped
when he's bad.

687
00:48:54,550 --> 00:48:59,520
When you're grown,

688
00:48:59,510 --> 00:49:02,710
