711
00:51:15,850 --> 00:51:18,680
Okay, but --
you know, and I can
see that now, so...

712
00:51:18,680 --> 00:51:20,480
Hon, hon.

713
00:51:20,480 --> 00:51:22,120
Ta-da!

714
00:51:22,110 --> 00:51:23,710
I...
I sold the car.

715
00:51:23,710 --> 00:51:25,670
